node.name: 6 days of relaxations
node.description: Take time out of busy everyday life, and immerse yourself in a state of total bliss on our relaxation & pampering spa holidays. Revitalize your system and enhance your well-being as you spoil yourself with indulgent spa treatments and therapies in the lap of luxury. Relax with massages, facials, body wraps and scrubs at award-winning spas for a whole new you. Take advantage of your peaceful surroundings by re-connecting with nature through outdoor meditation, to calm your body and mind. To achieve ultimate relaxation, learn to beat stress through the help of the wellness therapists, holistic yoga and meditation classes to return home feeling relaxed and rejuvenated.

node.name: Poroformula - reindeer ride for the whole family
node.briefDescription: Enjoy of a family frienly reindeer ride in Luosto, in Lapland!
node.description: During the Poroformula you will have chance to meet our friendly reindeers and test your reindeer racing skills with a full speed sleigh ride. After the 400 meters race you may participate in your new friend's feeding and hear interesting stories about your new friends. In the kota you will be  served strong lappish coffee, tasteful crowberry juice and homemade pastries. In addition you will have a nice certificate to prove your racing skills.
